17:54.641 --> 17:56.709
- Will you look at that?
- Gorgeous.

17:56.776 --> 17:59.212
Darling.

17:59.279 --> 18:01.147
I love your suit.

18:01.148 --> 18:02.249
Je l'aime bien!

18:07.620 --> 18:09.722
I'm shocked she got
out of bed this morning.

18:09.789 --> 18:11.158
