18:28.808 --> 18:30.410
I imagine you have.

18:30.477 --> 18:33.313
- Well, of course, we hate her.
- We've always hated her.

18:33.380 --> 18:34.890
I'm sure there are women
who can wear lipstick and rouge

18:34.914 --> 18:36.183
without looking like a Jezebel,

18:36.216 --> 18:37.593
but Eleanor Boardman
is not one of them.

18:37.617 --> 18:39.185
Her hemlines don't help.

18:39.186 --> 18:41.164
The real crime is her hair.
Who let her cut it all off?

18:41.188 --> 18:42.655
She says she did it
to be "modern."

18:42.722 --> 18:44.824
I heard it was a nasty
case of ringworm.

18:44.891 --> 18:46.193
Tallulah:
She rarely bathes.

18:46.226 --> 18:47.870
Eugenia: Is that why
she's been wearing a turban?

18:47.894 --> 18:49.196
