of fashion.

19:03.210 --> 19:05.312
Well, darling, it's not
like the lady is here.

19:05.378 --> 19:06.779
And it's not like
the lady's a lady.

19:06.846 --> 19:09.782
Maybe she is dreadful.
I don't know.

19:09.849 --> 19:12.385
