20:19.519 --> 20:20.787
Zelda?

20:43.443 --> 20:45.278
I haven't been married
in months.

20:45.345 --> 20:48.648
I feel like the whole thing's
over and done with.

20:48.715 --> 20:51.484
Marriage is a wonderful
institution, my boy.

20:51.551 --> 20:53.252
